title: xpost - automatically produce posts in jekyll
category: myprogram
tags: xpost, myprogram, git
---
It's a tool in shell script written by myself.
The script will format text file into html and automatically add header / footer as setted.
the output is a legal post file in jekyll

the code is upload to github: <a target=_blank href="https://github.com/xiechenny/xpost">get me</a>  (by chenny xie~)
